  m_text: "Assets\n\n\n\"Starter Tilemaps,\" \"Fruit+,\" & \"Font+ [Antiquity Print]\"\nBy
    SciGho\nhttps://ninjikin.itch.io/\n\n\"Fantasy Knight - Free Pixelart Animated
    Character\"\nBy aamatniekss\nhttps://aamatniekss.itch.io/\n\n\"Skeleton \u2014
    Enemy Asset\"\nBy Dotto-e\nhttps://dotto-e.itch.io/\n\n\"Basic Pixel Health bar
    and Scroll bar\" & \n\"Retro Pixel Ribbons, Banners and Frames 2\" \nBy BDragon1727\nhttps://bdragon1727.itch.io/\n\n\"Tiny
    RPG - Dragon Regalia GUI\"\nBy tiopalada\nhttps://tiopalada.itch.io/\n\n\"DungeonFont\"\nBy
    vrtxrry\nhttps://vrtxrry.itch.io/\n\n\"2D Pixel Heart\"\nBy BitGems\nhttps://shop.bitgem3d.com/products/pixel-hearts\n\n\n\nBackgrounds\n\n\n\"Heavy
    armored knight\"\nBy echerry\nhttps://www.artstation.com/echerryart\n\n\"[OC][CC]
    Buried Shrine (GIF)\"\nBy Jacob__V\nhttps://www.reddit.com/user/Jacob__V/\n\n\"Dungeon
    Card Game Art\"\nBy OLHA VOLKOVA\nhttps://www.artstation.com/olgavolkova\n\n\"Awareness
